    <text type="letter">
        <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_sf.00013.jpg" type="recto"/>     
        <body>
            <opener>  
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name> 
                    <date>Saturday Afternoon</date>
                    <date when="1888-07-21">July 21 '88
                        <ptr target="loc.03865_n1"/>
                    </date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Rather easier to-day&#8212;am writing a little &amp; at my proofs (the little
                new book <hi rend="italic">"Nov: Boughs"</hi><ptr target="n3999"/>)&#8212;have just rec'd three letters, one from my
                English friend Ernest Rhys,<ptr target="n4152"/> friend of Herbert Gilchrist,<ptr target="n0262"/> and one from Dr
                Bucke<ptr target="n0119"/>&#8212;Nothing special, but I will enclose them all (as I believe you are 
                entertain'd&#8212;like I am by such)<ptr target="loc.03865_n2"/>&#8212;I wish you to send the three back to me in the envelope&#8212;write
                a line to tell how you all [got] back&#8212;I liked your 
                visit&#8212;have enjoy'd the chicken&#8212;did you get back all right? did you get 
                the money all right at the bank?&#8212;pleasant weather here to-day&#8212;cloudy&#8212;</p>
               <p><date when="1888-07-21"><hi rend="underline">Sunday noon July 22</hi></date></p>
                <p>Am sitting up by the window&#8212;a little headache, &amp; heavy feeling&#8212;but
                I must take the thick with the thin&#8212;moderately cool &amp; rainy&#8212;very
                bearable for July&#8212;I am comfortable&#8212;good spirits&#8212;
            </p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
                <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc_sf.00014.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf003r" facs="loc_sf.00011.jpg" type="recto"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf004v" facs="loc_sf.00012.jpg" type="verso"/> 
            </closer>
        </body>
